videos.description: DeWanna Bonner does a nice fake on Allie Quigley and drains a 3-pointer.

videos.headline: Bonner fakes out Quigley to free herself for a 3

videos.description: The Sun's DeWanna Bonner gets the block, but the Sky's Courtney Vandersloot ends up with the ball and hits a 3-pointer.
